Restyaboard app is available on both And: Restyaboard app is available on both Android and iOS. Since the Restyaboard web application is already optimized for mobile display, the mobile apps are only an embedded web application + push notifications. Regular mobile apps are common for all instances. You'll need to enter an instance URL to get started (For more details, refer to %s ). Being a common app for multiple instances, push notifications are routed through our common proxy. Hence, you'll need to whitelist your server IP with us. Though we don't intercept the push messages, if you're worried about data privacy, please %s offering.
